cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and word representations. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it uses neural networks and vector representations. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as word representations are often used in information retrieval tasks, and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it uses neural networks.
